<!--이름/ 키 / 몸무게 / 소속팀 / 이미지 1~4 / 동영상-->
<h1>등록된 선수목록을 보여줍니다.</h1>

<div class='row'>
  <% @players.each do |player| %>
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-xl-3">
      <a href = "/players/<%= player.id %>">  
        <div class="card h-card">
          <div class="h-img-wrapper">
            <% if !player.image1.blank? %>
              <img class="card-img-top h-img" src="<%= player.image1 %>" alt="Card image cap">
            <% else %>
              <%= image_tag("placeholder_fest.jpeg", class: "card-img-top h-img") %>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="h-card-title" style="color:#09083a;"><%= player.name %></h5>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  
</div>
<br>

<%= link_to '선수등록', new_player_path %>